{"tid":326126,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【劉曉波病逝】頭七全球哀悼 支聯會周三晚添馬公園舉行追思會","createTime":"2017-07-17T17:44:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T11:41:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5a83f89095d553a7ce5b3a9bd44096976a4405fc","tid":326126,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T17:44:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170717/56966841\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170717%2F56966841&d=RH%2FvP3SnK6T%2F1sH3IxiJipUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=c6ba7dff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170717%2F56966841&h=59074ab2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170717/56966841</a><br />\n<br />\n【劉曉波病逝】頭七全球哀悼 支聯會周三晚添馬公園舉行追思會<br />\n<br />\n33,463<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 0717 16:15<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170717/large/1500279319_4168.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170717%2Flarge%2F1500279319_4168.jpg&h=5bc36b94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n被中共囚禁至死的諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波上周四(13日)病逝，關注劉的團體「自由劉曉波工作組」號召全球民眾，在周三（19日）其頭七當晚北京時間8時自發公祭劉曉波，建議各地民眾擺放空凳，然後進行默哀、三鞠躬，並且豎舉三指，寓意抗爭、自由、希望，空凳上可擺放任何一件祭奠物。<br />\n<br />\n於本港，支聯會亦正構思在劉曉波頭七晚上舉行追思活動，副主席蔡耀昌表示，並非為了響應號召舉辦，一直都有相關構思，暫定會在周三晚上8時於金鐘添馬公園舉行「劉曉波頭七追思會」，細節容後公佈，呼籲市民參與。此外香港天主教正義和平委員會明晚8時亦會為劉曉波舉行追思彌撒，地點於西灣河聖十字徑1號聖十字架堂。"},{"pid":"782cf022384e21db89dffeb80bcd607f731c561a","tid":326126,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T18:10:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ichef-1.bbci.co.uk/news/976/cpsprodpb/DE99/production/_96858965_b9ff2c91-623d-41fa-a07d-209f8b347908.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef-1.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F976%2Fcpsprodpb%2FDE99%2Fproduction%2F_96858965_b9ff2c91-623d-41fa-a07d-209f8b347908.jpg&h=693daad9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20121207/large/07ce101p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20121207%2Flarge%2F07ce101p.jpg&h=c68d5bdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/renquanfazhi/xl1-10082015114227.html/5218971e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfa.org%2Fmandarin%2Fyataibaodao%2Frenquanfazhi%2Fxl1-10082015114227.html%2F5218971e.jpg&h=a84318fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a05e92c26a66f82d6614101a31c64d1bfc8472fa","tid":326126,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T01:14:24.000Z","msg":"今晚八點"},{"pid":"5773e27c192ae6f14afddd282985ada1f46d03fb","tid":326126,"uid":64948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T01:24:54.000Z","msg":"一死就搶住出來食人血饅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c793bc0e98b09e790b81c1c21543dc5b2a2b6b9","tid":326126,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T06:04:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今晚八點</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/20108176_1568865283147897_3159034887357253126_n.jpg?oh=513e69d0f38bc5329fab587a872f4aa5&amp;oe=59C76059\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F20108176_1568865283147897_3159034887357253126_n.jpg%3Foh%3D513e69d0f38bc5329fab587a872f4aa5%26oe%3D59C76059&h=59eae97c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89a97d7e04e630fd88381b75dd3c7bce602f4a04","tid":326126,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T09:59:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一死就搶住出來食人血饅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得可以每年搞一次同劉曉波造忌<br />\n<br />\n永續CAP水